# Cargo build artifacts for the peppyos-shared workspace.
target

# Cargo.lock IS committed for this workspace (deliberately not ignored). It runs
# its own test suite, which benefits from reproducible dependency resolution, and
# it builds & ships peppylib-py's native extension (an end artifact embedded and
# deployed by consumers). A library's lockfile is ignored by downstream consumers,
# so committing it is safe for reuse. See the root .gitignore for the policy note.
